	  Distribution 
 
	Put your flyers, brochures, CD-ROMs or other materials directly into the hands of your target audience. You can even target specified countries -  contact us  for details. 
 
	 
		 
			 
				Insert type 
			 
				Price per thousand* 
		 
		 
			 
